steps.name: I Launch the parasBank Site
Input the User Name and password and click login "Sam1" and "123"
Navigate to Open New Account section
I Select the Account Type "CHECKING" and Click Open new accountButton
A New account is opened
I Click the Transfer Funds option
Input the Amount 20 to be transferred
Select the Account from which transfer to happen
Click TransferButton
Fund transfer is complete
I Click the Accounts Overview Option
Select the Account from the table
Details of the Account Displayed
Account activity details displayed is exported to excel
I Click Logout option
Successfully logged out from parasbank Site
